{"_path":"/maps/_person/shunyu-yao","_dir":"_person","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"姚顺雨 (Shunyu Yao)","description":"OpenAI 前研究员、AI Agent 方向核心探索者，现任腾讯首席 AI 科学家","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"姚顺雨（1998 年出生），本科毕业于清华大学交叉信息研究院\"姚班\"，普林斯顿大学计算机科学博士，师从 NLP 领域知名学者 Karthik Narasimhan。博士期间在 Google Brain 和 OpenAI 实习，2023 年加入 OpenAI 任研究员，2025 年入选《麻省理工科技评论》\"35 岁以下科技创新 35 人\"中国区名单。2025 年底加入腾讯，任 CEO/总裁办公室首席 AI 科学家，兼任 AI Infra 部及大语言模型部负责人。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"主要贡献观点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要贡献/观点？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 的\"下半场\"理论"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提出 AI 发展已进入\"中场休息\"阶段，核心特征是从\"训练大于评估\"转向\"评估大于训练\"。上半场通过算法创新（反向传播、Transformer、GPT-3 等）不断刷分；下半场需要重新定义问题，构建能衡量真实世界效用的评估体系。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Language Agent 的倡导者"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"指出 Agent 的本质是通过语言实现推理，通过推理实现泛化，是通往 AGI 的必经形态。提出 ReAct（Reasoning + Acting）框架，将思考作为行动空间的一部分，显著提升了 Agent 的泛化能力。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"效用问题（Utility Problem）"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"指出当前 AI 的核心矛盾：模型在 MMLU、Codeforces 等基准上达到博士水平，却未能显著改变 GDP。原因在于评估设定追求\"难题\"而非\"实用\"，学术界缺乏评估\"学习能力\"而非\"现有能力\"的基准。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agent 记忆的重要性"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"强调 AI 系统的记忆层次缺陷：仅有上下文（短期记忆）和模型权重（长期记忆），缺乏人类式的灵活记忆巩固机制。认为这是限制 Agent 持续学习和个性化的关键瓶颈。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"代表作品"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代表作品？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《The Second Half》(2025) - 阐述 AI 下半场理论的代表性博文"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2210.03629","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ReAct: Synergizing Reasoning and Acting in Language Models"}]},{"type":"text","value":" (2022) - 将推理与行动结合的 Agent 框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2205.11916","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Language Models are Few-Shot Reasoners"}]},{"type":"text","value":" (2022) - 上下文学习研究"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ysymyth.github.io/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"个人主页"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ysymyth.github.io/The-Second-Half/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Second Half 原文"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_person:shunyu-yao.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_person/shunyu-yao.md","_stem":"6.maps/_person/shunyu-yao","_extension":"md"}